        "Shadow","Shiny","Shocked","Silver","SpiritSparkle","Solar","Soulflame","Sparkling","Spectral","Starlit","Stellar","Storm",
        "Tempest","Tethered","Tiny","Toxic","Tranquil","Twilight",
        "UFO",
